Cost-volume filtering parameters:


     radius: radius of the guided filter (1)
     alpha: value of alpha (0.9)
     epsilon: regularization parameter (6.5025)
     tau1: max for color difference (7)
     tau2: max for gradient difference (2)

     radius: radius of the weighted median filter (1)
     sigmac: value of sigma_color (25.5)
     sigmas: value of sigma_space (9)

Execution:
 ./bin/otbStereoFiltersTestDriver main_CostVolumeFilter Radius Min_Disp Max_Disp
 Left_Image(3bands) Right_Image(3bands) Path_Of_Outputs_Images/ 



Patch Match Stéréo parameters:

  radius: size of patch (35)
  alpha: value of alpha (0.9) 
  tau1: max for color difference (10)
  tau2: max for gradient difference (2)

Execution:
./bin/otbStereoFiltersTestDriver main_PatchMatch radius dispMin dispMax
  Left_Image(3bands) Right_Image(3bands) Path_Of_Outputs_Images/


 

